{"tid":687881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭丈夫辱罵求償962萬　她勝訴反賠更多錢","createTime":"2018-06-02T15:55:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T01:08:31.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"583a202ff4b4c0aa8067c31769b383fd81d47fb6","tid":687881,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:55:36.000Z","msg":"贏了官司，反而賠更多！<br />\n日前《蘋果日報》報導，台北呂姓房仲婚後和李姓妻子簽下「婚姻保證書」，承諾不得對妻子言語及肢體暴力，事後卻多次罵妻髒話，還嫌妻做的飯菜比前女友做的難吃，結果遭妻罰寫悔過書並提告求償962萬元違約金。呂男辯稱，他的房產已給妻子，每月薪資還要被扣繳，如今又遭妻趕出家門，實在沒有錢。士林地院認定呂男確實違約，只是違約金太高，今判他僅須賠償妻子12萬元。<br />\n《自由時報》報導，法官認定李妻索賠金額過高，改為以每次違規須賠3萬元計算，最終依4次言語污辱判賠12萬元，但李女須負擔本案9萬多元裁判費，加上律師費用，雖贏得官司但其實賠了更多錢，全案還可上訴。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/235512_867aba41e49dd9cb74d80292046fcdf9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F235512_867aba41e49dd9cb74d80292046fcdf9.png&h=be09c41a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180602/1365704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180602%2F1365704&d=sMYxUHRkZZkXU%2BYeR80TAv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6403d663\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180602%2F1365704&h=85589e09\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180602/1365704</a>"},{"pid":"ef0afeb8b3d770de8d75edb5bb9a920ee7e1e625","tid":687881,"uid":86756,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:21:18.000Z","msg":"屌 8字波"},{"pid":"aace20aca2b3f5bd9aae708b50883de2ac35c3c0","tid":687881,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:26:08.000Z","msg":"下下都係拎男方著數 以後識有後生仔敢結婚"},{"pid":"071b4ddba2ce2eabc7b9824ff59fa5c1179805ae","tid":687881,"uid":56533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:26:27.000Z","msg":"最終依4次言語污辱判賠12萬元，但李女須負擔本案9萬多元裁判費，加上律師費用，雖贏得官司但其實賠了更多錢，全案還可上訴。<br />\n<br />\n法院&amp;律師成最大嬴家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da97ad421242fd79e5d9f07b81c43d9f6927056","tid":687881,"uid":80243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:29:47.000Z","msg":"簽呢個保證書同做狗有咩分別,除咗唔用暴力，言語暴力龍門任人舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5b4e789029d7c50bac6b9d380ce947d8fa759e","tid":687881,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T01:08:31.000Z","msg":"推post"}]}